UPower Release Notes

1. Write NEWS entries for UPower in the same format as usual.

git shortlog UPOWER_0_99_4.. | grep -i -v trivial | grep -v Merge > NEWS.new

Version 0.99.5
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2017-xx-xx

New Features:
Bugfixes:

2. Commit changes to git:

git commit -a -m "Released UPower 0.99.5"
git tag -s -f -m "Released UPower 0.99.5" UPOWER_0_99_5
<wait>
git push --tags
git push

3. Generate the tarball:

make dist

4. Upload tarball:

scp *.tar.* hughsient@annarchy.freedesktop.org:/srv/upower.freedesktop.org/www/releases/

5. Do post release version bump in configure.ac

6. Commit changes:

git commit -a -m "trivial: post release version bump"
git push

7. Send an email to devkit-devel@lists.freedesktop.org

